Output demo.gif
Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 650
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type "source .venv/bin/activate && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "jadwal sample --region gulf"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "jadwal regions"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "jadwal generate --count 3 --region egypt --json"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 2s
